| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2025-0312 — Recovery Inhibition (dragonforce)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 1f569b78-1edc-59cd-a75d-23c1621ee7d8"
